CustomField.description: Used to tell if this is a new or rework cycle on a Lead or Contact for scaleMatters.
CustomField.formula: IF( AND( TEXT(Cycle_Type__c) = "New", TEXT(Cycle_Object__c) = "Lead" ), "7ea3d6e3caa94e07a5a8f20a864d6f23", IF( AND( TEXT(Cycle_Type__c) = "Rework", TEXT(Cycle_Object__c) = "Lead" ), "c6faa56d91224e06a79783428474c5c7", IF( AND( TEXT(Cycle_Type__c) = "New", TEXT(Cycle_Object__c) = "Contact" ), "fb9489e422904a2f964c604dcad51b4d", IF( AND( TEXT(Cycle_Type__c) = "Rework", TEXT(Cycle_Object__c) = "Contact" ), "05e7ce3501f14dfbbdce2857cba57cc2", NULL ) ) ) )
